♥️🎶Moment of Overcoming. 🎶♥️
Today, singing “Torn” with @davidmartinsn, who also just learned alone, with willpower and dedication that inspires me, I felt very happy! Music brings me happiness and I always loved singing, but I was ashamed to “let my voice go” in front of others, because I was always mocked by those who listened. So today, with a perfect voice / tone or not, the great value, is my overcoming, not only finding myself enjoying accompanying singing with my boyfriend playing guitar, but sharing it with you, too.
Today, even more, I understand that as a couple, the value of wanting to “sing / dance” together sharing on reciprocity in listening with sensitivity, learning, supporting, encouraging, appreciating, inspiring, expanding, extracting and naturally awakening the best we have and are like human being and couple is really essential. I am very grateful to share such magical moments @davidmartinsn Thank you for the companionship and for everything I am learning and growing with you. ♥️
And let’s keep listening only what makes us happy and with our heart fulfilled. 
✨
♥🎶Momento de superação. 🎶 ♥ ️Hoje, cantando “Torn” com @davidmartinsn , que também acabou de aprender sozinho, com uma força de vontade e dedicação que me inspira, me senti muito feliz! Música me traz felicidade e sempre gostei muito de cantar, mas tinha vergonha de “soltar a voz” na frente dos outros, pois sempre fui zoada por quem ouvia. Já hoje, com voz/tom perfeito ou não, o grande valor é a minha superação, não só de estar achando gostoso em acompanhar cantando, o meu namorado tocando violão, mas compartilhando isso com vocês, também. Hoje, ainda mais, entendo que como casal, o valor em querer “cantar/ dançar” juntos na reciprocidade em ouvir com sensibilidade, aprender, apoiar, incentivar, apreciar, inspirar,  expandir, extrair e naturalmente despertar o melhor que temos/ somos como ser humano e casal é realmente essencial. Sou muito grata em compartilhar momentos tão mágicos @davidmartinsn . Obrigada pelo companheirismo e por tudo o que aprendo e cresço com você! E vamos continuar ouvindo apenas o que nos deixa felizes e com nosso coração sati
